OB: Marked lines left (starting at large
Oak on left), right (starting at large Oak
on right), long and beyond; Traditional
golf green right of tee.

OB: Marked lines left, right, long
and beyond.
Mandatory: Discs must not enter
restricted plane right of 1st marked tree or
left of 2nd marked tree. If either MANDO is
missed, proceed to corresponding DZ
+1 penalty throw.
Notes: Tree(s) denoted with (*) are
surrounded by marked Relief Area(s).

beyond; Maintenance yard on right;
Traditional golf greens.

restricted plane right of marked tree.

+1 penalty throw.
Notes: Marked Relief Area around tree
(~50’ right of FPO tee / ~350’ in front
of MPO tee) designates an active
honey bee hive.
